      57.96,
      589.87,
      534.41,
      703.78
    ],
    "text": "Winds: Winds will be South-westerly or Westerly in direction. Wind speed will be (25-35) kmph. Wind speed can increase up to (40-45) kmph at times in the sea areas off the coast extending from Galle to Pottuvil via Matara and Hambantota. State of Sea: The sea areas off the coast extending from Galle to Pottuvil via Matara and Hambantota may be fairly rough at times. The other sea areas around the island may be slight or Moderate.",
